quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  50,28,"(Allāhu) yóò sọ pé: “Ẹ má se ṣàríyànjiyàn lọ́dọ̀ Mi. Mo kúkú ti ṣe ìlérí fún yín ṣíwájú."
  50,29,"Wọn kò sì lè yí ọ̀rọ̀ náà padà ní ọ̀dọ̀ Mi. Èmi kò sì níí ṣe àbòsí sí àwọn ẹrú Mi.”"
  50,30,"(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí A óò sọ fún iná Jahanamọ pé: Ṣèbí o ti kún?” Ó sì máa sọ pé: “Ṣèbí àfikún tún wà?”"
  51,22,"Arísìkí yín àti ohun tí À ń ṣe ní àdéhùn fún yín wà nínú sánmọ̀."
  51,23,"Nítorí náà, Mó fi Olúwa sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ búra, dájúdájú òdodo ni (ọ̀rọ̀ náà) gẹ́gẹ́ bí ó ṣe jẹ́ òdodo pé ẹ̀ ń fẹnu sọ̀rọ̀."
  51,24,"Ǹjẹ́ ọ̀rọ̀ àwọn àlejò (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm, àwọn alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé, ti dé ọ̀dọ̀ rẹ?"
  52,13,"(Rántí) ọjọ́ tí wọn yóò máa tì wọ́n lọ́ sínú iná Jahanamọ ní ìtìkutì."
  52,14,"Èyí ni Iná náà tí ẹ̀ ń pè ní irọ́."
  52,15,"Ṣé idán ni èyí ni tàbí ẹ̀yin kò ríran?"
  53,7,"nígbà tí ó wà nínú òfurufú lókè pátápátá."
  53,8,"Lẹ́yìn náà, ó sún mọ́ (Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -). Ó sì sọ̀kalẹ̀ (tọ̀ ọ́ wá)."
  53,9,"(Àlàfo ààrin àwọn méjèèjì) sì tó ìwọ̀n ọrún ọfà méjì, tàbí kí ó kéré (sí ìyẹn).1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-Baƙọrah;  2:74.]
